<p>In this we are using external style sheet named <span>"style.css"</span> and then we provide different styles for different tags.</p>
<img class="imag1" src="img.jpg" alt="img" width="240" height="240">
<img class="imag2" src="img.jpg" alt="img" width="240" height="240">
<img class="imag3" src="img.jpg" alt="img" width="240" height="240">
<div>
<h4>This is the div tag..!!!</h4>
<p id="para">This divides the element as a block or a container and also has a "id" named as "para".</p>
<p>In this I'm gona define a time tag..<time datetime="2025-09-01 09:00">Today's date</time>.. it displays only the content..</p>
<h4>This is the end of div tag..!!!</h4>
